title: Monte Pittman Solo Discography
description:
Monte Pittman solo discography
Bit Rate: Various (128-320 kbps)
Includes cover art

Acoustic & Live and Covers may not be complete. These are the only files that I have found on Monte's youtube and soundcloud in 2012. Some files do not have great quality. I am aware, so please do not complain. The reason they are on here is to have as complete of a discography. I hope you enjoy!
